Author: Dibaba Bayisa Gemechu [aut, cre],
  Legesse Kassa Debusho [aut],
  Linda Haines [aut]
Maintainer: Dibaba Bayisa Gemechu <diboobayu@gmail.com>
Depends: R (>= 3.4.0), MASS, Matrix, igraph, tcltk
License: GPL-2
Description: Computes Bayesian A- and D-optimal block designs under the linear mixed effects model settings using block/array exchange algorithm of Debusho, Gemechu and Haines (2018) <doi:10.1080/03610918.2018.1429617> and Gemechu, Debusho and Haines (2025) <doi:10.5539/ijsp.v14n1p50> where the interest is in a 
	comparison of all possible elementary treatment contrasts. The package also provides an optional 
	method of using the graphical user interface (GUI) R package 'tcltk' to ensure that it is user friendly.
